'''天主教亞特蘭大總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidiocesis Atlantensis}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Atlanta}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國三十二個總教區之一。

總教區管轄[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]西北部六十九個縣，並轄四個教區。總教區教座位於州府[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]，2010年時有教友850,000人、87個堂區和280名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|額我略·若望·哈特邁爾|Gregory John Hartmayer|額我略·J·哈特邁爾}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 05.03.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/05/200305a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305124430/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/05/200305a.html |archivedate=2020-03-05 |language=en |date=2020-03-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|岳厄爾·瑪竇·康曾|Joel Matthias Konzen|岳厄爾·M·康曾}}和{{link-en|伯爾納鐸·什萊辛格|Bernard Shlesinger|伯爾納鐸·E·什萊辛格三世}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Current Bishops of the Archdiocese of Atlanta |url=https://archatl.com/about/archbishop-and-bishops/ |publisher=The Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Atlanta |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712143025/https://archatl.com/about/archbishop-and-bishops/ |archivedate=2019-07-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

'''亞特蘭大教區'''於1956年7月2日從薩凡納-亞特蘭大教區分出而成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXIII |year=1956 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |accessdate=2020-01-24 |language=la |pages=750-752 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421185405/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1962年2月10日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=III |volume=V |year=1963 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=919-920 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-55-1963-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-01-24 |language=la |archive-date=2020-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422123821/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-55-1963-ocr.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

